Package: markovtext
Type: Package
Title: Generate Random Text Using Markov Chains
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Belanger
Maintainer: Christopher Belanger <christopher.a.belanger@gmail.com>
Description: An extremely unserious package for generating random text using
     probabilistic Markov chains based on arbitrary input text.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
